2021-04-16T02:58:58.000Z","msg":"知唔知邊間麵包鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4b92c25136bca6d177649fd0ad81d8ebb9b36e","tid":2490903,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:59:03.000Z","msg":"612基金仲爭一千萬先夠cover今個月開支<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2490867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2490867</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9b0d535232280be9e2f13e08f7297ca57ac93cfd","tid":2490903,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:59:22.000Z","msg":"以我嘅司法認知，哈林同庾澄慶係唔同嘅嘢"},{"pid":"daec5af81d45976a784f4ae033ba50a8971dde93","tid":2490903,"uid":140246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:59:47.000Z","msg":"蛋卷,卷蛋 ,,瑞士卷<br />\n<br />\n同一樣野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c27b3a7bef733e1cb2143e373008d0e689ed0ad","tid":2490903,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"蛋卷 定 卷蛋"},{"pid":"14b5033bc67ffe4e14e0a0169dc57b188bdff469","tid":2490903,"uid":41411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"個個都唔撚同叫法架啦<br />\n不嬲D人會叫瑞士卷做卷蛋/蛋卷<br />\n冰箱同冰格係咪又係2樣野呀<br />\n弱智都可以做官"},{"pid":"5fb909004fa6f138087d6c00508f043ff72cc034","tid":2490903,"uid":464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc5cc28960d4f3ec06853273ee777d71c41ddd88","tid":2490903,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:56:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2379947/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2379947/page/1</a><br />\n瑞士卷叫左幾十年 近年係咪得支那引入先叫卷蛋？<br />\n<br />\n之前先討論過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:00:05.000Z","msg":"卷蛋 蛋卷 瑞士卷<br />\n唔同人會唔同叫法<br />\n但係個場景/對象係麵包舖 麵包師傅<br />\n一定知道講緊邊樣 係個法官唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e00515018200f2205d7ab9877ba697c2c22908","tid":2490903,"uid":255940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:01:06.000Z","msg":"我既司法認知同佢既司法認知唔撚同<br />\n鳩up做裁決仲要扮係專業判斷<br />\n無罪假定唔見佢講"},{"pid":"58d3b4d30e4ccdd393abcd241ab48a4c1dfc54b8","tid":2490903,"uid":314719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:01:27.000Z","msg":"明顯個官諗蛋卷係過年食果啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8639011b7b9381236952a9ad51783487ad38b3a","tid":2490903,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:01:34.000Z","msg":"其實拎來整蛋卷同瑞士卷又有咩分別<br />\n大家咪又係麵包舖產品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fdc98a337df4354d607720965dba5c30ce9117","tid":2490903,"uid":41411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:01:44.000Z","msg":"黨報東方都報過呀屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20190323/bkn-20190323150026180-0323_00982_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190323%2Fbkn-20190323150026180-0323_00982_001.html&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=3222c9a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20190323/bkn-20190323150026180-0323_00982_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【Food Stop】瑞士卷叫「卷蛋」定「蛋卷」？<br />\n2019年03月23日(六) 15:00<br />\n<br />\n瑞士卷英文名叫Swiss Roll，但其實並非起源於瑞士，有說是由奧地利人創作，日本人則稱之為Roll Cake，海綿蛋糕包裹着忌廉及生果餡料，鬆軟好味。（資料圖片）<br />\n1/3<br />\n最近與朋友飯局時因為討論一個問題而拗得面紅耳熱，以為大家議論國家大事嗎？非也，雖然我美食婷一向關心時事，但一班人食飯還是適合傾一些輕鬆的話題，點知雙方最後都各持己見，仲話要放上網睇吓誰是誰非。<br />\n<br />\n問題就是：你會叫瑞士卷做卷蛋還是蛋卷？<br />\n<br />\n答案看似簡單，但原來兩種叫法都各有支持者，而且雙方都堅持自己的叫法才是正確。網上公投結果以「卷蛋派」佔大多數，也有人堅持只叫瑞士卷，至於「蛋卷派」雖然勢孤力弱，不過都能夠找到證據，的確有不少舊式冰室稱瑞士卷為蛋卷。<br />\n<br />\n究竟哪個叫法才正確？不如先「問下」搜尋網站。無論輸入瑞士卷或卷蛋，均會彈出Swiss Roll的圖片和解說，也就是包着忌廉餡料的海綿捲蛋糕。輸入蛋卷的話，則顯示長條形的金黃香脆雞蛋卷，與瑞士卷毫無關係。<br />\n<br />\n網上資料未必百分百準確，為了尋根究柢，於是美食婷我又走去問<span class=\"red\">連鎖冰室老闆徐汶緯，他解釋以前很多冰室都會把瑞士卷這種用雞蛋做的蛋糕直譯為Egg Roll，因此人們就叫它蛋卷</span>；不過當大家都知道瑞士卷的英文其實是Swiss Roll後，新式的茶餐廳及麵包店通常都會採用瑞士卷或卷蛋兩個叫法。"},{"pid":"a3f4405d2f31c7991b6f07676be6dcc5b9601689","tid":2490903,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:01:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"966d8e1040026e2ac3ef4e782b83a43f80bbad11","tid":2490903,"uid":185045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:02:38.000Z","msg":"衝出黎話自己無知"},{"pid":"4eb8111276f9a132e7c441c6fe9d1fa4b6851ea7","tid":2490903,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58d3b4d30e4ccdd393abcd241ab48a4c1dfc54b8","tid":2490903,"uid":314719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:01:27.000Z","msg":"明顯個官諗蛋卷係過年食果啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:02:43.000Z","msg":"其實㠪常邏輯來講<br />\n拎來整呢隻蛋卷都冇問題架<br />\n咪又係要碌平佢"},{"pid":"59098fe11b6291b8fa91f3cde63714a9cda17b52","tid":2490903,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eb8111276f9a132e7c441c6fe9d1fa4b6851ea7","tid":2490903,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58d3b4d30e4ccdd393abcd241ab48a4c1dfc54b8","tid":2490903,"uid":314719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:01:27.000Z","msg":"明顯個官諗蛋卷係過年食果啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:02:43.000Z","msg":"其實㠪常邏輯來講<br />\n拎來整呢隻蛋卷都冇問題架<br />\n咪又係要碌平佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:03:11.000Z","msg":"正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c80238c908771ee1d1129cdbdb7a6beb7665cbc","tid":2490903,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:03:35.000Z","msg":"用咁撚樣既理由就駁回上訴<br />\n真係痴撚線"}]}